'''''PLAYERUNKNOWN'S BATTLEGROUNDS Mobile''''' (abbreviated '''''PUBG Mobile''''') is an online multiplayer mobile battle royale game developed by [[Lightspeed & Quantum Studios]] and published by [[Tencent Games]].

It was released on February 9th, 2018 in China as '''''PUBG: Exhilarating Battlefield'''''.  Following a soft launch in Canada, an English version of Exhilarating Battlefield, localized simply as PUBG Mobile, was released worldwide on March 19th, 2018.

